title: Palakkattu Madhavan
subTitle: Madhavan, frustrated by his wife Lakshmi's success, adopts Pattu Maami, an elderly woman, for financial gain. But as their bond grows, Madhavan faces unexpected life changes and emotional growth.

title: Engal Thanga Raja
subTitle: Manjula falls in love with Raja but he is scared to reciprocate his feelings. Later, he discovers that Manjula's father is the same man who destroyed his sister's life.

title: Kattu Paya Sir Intha Kaali
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Chinna
subTitle: Chinna, a gangster, changes his way of life after he falls in love with Gayatri. However, he ends up in jail after he kills a gang leader in order to save Gayatri.

title: Vietnam Colony
subTitle: A real estate company appoints Krishnamurthy to vacate a colony, claiming it is filled with anti-social elements. He gradually realises that the company is being unjust to its residents.

title: Chinna Thayee
subTitle: Rasamma strives to ensure a proper life for her daughter Chinna, who is born out of wedlock. But her worst fear comes true when her daughter follows her footsteps and falls in love with a rich man.

title: Vetri Malai
subTitle: Jeeva and Madhavi live with their dad and stepmother. Jeeva marries Raja, while Madhavi is visually impaired and has trouble getting married. Madhavi's life takes a turn when she meets Raja's friend.

title: Paarai
subTitle: Durai Raj, a lorry driver, has only one friend, Jayaram. However, when his friend dies, Durai Raj strives to support his family.
